---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Experiences - Talia Sable" description="Date experiences and adventures">
  <div class="hero">
    <img src="/header-pink.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" class="hero-image" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <article class="experiences">
    <h1>Experiences</h1>

    <div class="experiences-content">
        <section class="game-intro">
          <h2>Let's Play</h2>
          <p>I love novelty and unusual experiences. They're what make life interesting. This point system is my way of encouraging the kind of dates that excite me: trying something new, going somewhere beautiful, or doing something we'll both remember.</p>
          <p>Rack up points by taking me on adventures. Collect enough and unlock a reward, like your next overnight at the 16-hour rate instead of the 24-hour cost.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="points-with-image">
          <section class="points-system">
            <h2>How to Score Points</h2>

            <div class="point-category">
            <h3>Food & Drink</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Michelin-starred restaurant: <strong>1 point per star</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="point-category">
            <h3>Travel & Adventure</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Flying to a new country together: <strong>10 points</strong></li>
              <li>Overnight train ride: <strong>8 points</strong></li>
              <li>Hot springs in Iceland or fjords in Norway: <strong>15 points</strong></li>
              <li>Weekend in Bali, Mexico City, or Japan: <strong>12 points</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="point-category">
            <h3>Culture & Fun</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Runway show: <strong>10 points</strong></li>
              <li>Strip club: <strong>4 points</strong></li>
              <li>Gallery opening or museum: <strong>3 points</strong></li>
              <li>City Museum in St. Louis: <strong>6 points</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="point-category">
            <h3>Unique Experiences</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Mile high club in a private jet: <strong>20 points</strong></li>
              <li>Milking a cow: <strong>5 points</strong></li>
              <li>Shopping date (Issey Miyake, Miu Miu, Bottega): <strong>4 points</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          </section>

          <div class="points-image">
            <img src="/body-bluedress.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="rewards">
          <h2>Rewards</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>24 points:</strong> Your next 24-hour date at the 16-hour rate ($12k instead of $17k)</li>
            <li><strong>40 points:</strong> Weekend getaway at full day pricing ($17k/night instead of full weekend rate)</li>
            <li><strong>60 points:</strong> Five-day vacation at weekend pricing</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="dream-dates">
          <h2>Dream Dates</h2>
          <p>I'm an ambivert: a cozy night in is as good as a night out. But if we're adventuring:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Start at a chill bar with sour cocktails</li>
            <li><strong>SF:</strong> Lazy Bear, Quince, Atelier Crenn</li>
            <li><strong>NYC:</strong> Jungsik, Le Coucou, Carbone</li>
            <li>Anywhere with great Vietnamese, Japanese, or Italian</li>
            <li>Shopping: Issey Miyake, Cult Gaia, Miu Miu, L'Agence, Bottega Veneta</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
  </article>

  <div class="footer-image">
    <img src="/header-backyard.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    width: 100%;
    height: 60vh;
    min-height: 400px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
  }

  .experiences {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .experiences h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .experiences-content {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .game-intro,
  .points-system,
  .rewards,
  .dream-dates {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .game-intro {
    background-color: rgba(184, 134, 11, 0.1);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .game-intro h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .game-intro p {
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  section h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  section p {
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .points-with-image {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .points-image {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 2rem);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .points-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .point-category {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .point-category:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .point-category h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  li strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .rewards {
    background-color: rgba(74, 37, 69, 0.05);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .rewards ul {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .rewards li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .footer-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 60vh;
    min-height: 400px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .footer-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      height: 50vh;
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .experiences {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .points-with-image {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .points-image {
      position: static;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .point-category h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
